long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
AutoFyl is a browser extension designed to streamline online form completion, saving users time and minimizing errors. By automatically populating forms with pre-set information, AutoFyl enhances efficiency and ensures accuracy across various web interactions.

Key Features:
	•	Auto Form Filling: Automatically fills out forms with your pre-set information, reducing manual input and the risk of errors.
	•	Cross-Browser Support: Ensures a consistent experience across multiple browsers.
	•	Time-Saving: Significantly cuts down the time spent on repetitive form-filling tasks.
	•	Secure Data Storage: Your data is stored locally in your browser, ensuring privacy and security.

Frequently Asked Questions:
	1.	What do I get exactly? Access to features based on your chosen plan, including form filling and email generation.
	2.	Is it compatible with all browsers? Yes, AutoFyl works seamlessly across multiple browsers.
	3.	How secure is my data? Your data is stored locally in your browser and is not accessible to us.
	4.	Can I customize which forms AutoFyl works with? Customization options are available to suit your needs.
	5.	What makes you different from other auto-fill extensions? AutoFyl offers a combination of AI generations, secure data storage, and cross-browser support.
	6.	How often is AutoFyl updated? Regular updates ensure compatibility and feature enhancements.
	7.	Can I get a refund? Refund policies are outlined in our terms and conditions.
	8.	How can I get support if I have issues? Contact us via our website or email for assistance.

AutoFyl simplifies online interactions by automating form completion, allowing you to focus on more important tasks. Choose the plan that best fits your needs and experience the convenience of effortless form filling.
